text: Tarsals are bones found in the feet. They are also known as ankle bones. There are seven of them in each foot. The seven tarsals are: * Medial cuneiform * Intermediate cuneiform * Lateral cuneiform * Navicular * Talus * Calcaneus * Cuboid ==Related pages== * Metatarsals * Phalanges * Bones of the foot * Ankle * Foot Category:Bones of the foot
title: Tarsals
